Package: ampliconR
Title: Analysis of 16S rRNA Sequencing Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("First", "Last", , "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: R package for analysis of 16S rRNA sequencing data, based on
    scripts from Sorbie, Delgado Jimenez and Benakis (2022) and Sorbie,
    Delgado Jimenez, Weiler and Benakis (2023). Provides functions for data
    import, normalization, alpha and beta diversity analysis, differential
    abundance testing, and visualization.
